These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, backgammon, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
House: futuristic, tower, gothic-revival, cape-cod
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, purple, chestnut, apricot
1. the tower house is the fan of techno##1
2. the gothic-revival house is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing canasta##2
3. the tower house is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the futuristic house##1
6. the person who likes chestnut is the person playing backgammon##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
8. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
9. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Game   | whist | canasta   | monopoly  | backgammon  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| House   | cape-cod | tower | gothic-revival | futuristic |
| Color     | apricot  | green       | purple    | chestnut     |

