.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, british, malaysian, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, canasta, go
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, february, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the russian##1
2. the turkish is on the far right##1
3. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the malaysian is on the right of the british##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person playing canasta and the person who's birthday is in july##2
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person watching western movies and the person playing go##2
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the malaysian##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality         | russian | british    | malaysian  | turkish    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Game           | go      | canasta       | billiard      | mah-jongg       |
| Birthday         | august    | june | february | july |

