.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, techno, punk, soul
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, billiard, bridge
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cycling, tennis, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is the person playing bridge##1
7. the fan of soul is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the fan of r&b is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing bridge##2
9. the person playing billiard is between the fan of punk and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre        | techno | punk     | r&b   | soul     |
| Game       | snooker   | scrabble   | billiard | bridge |
| Sport         | skiing   | tennis | soccer       | cycling    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

