 5. the dannemann-smoker is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 7. the game-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the blend-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is between the owner of the bird and the person traveling to boston##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| City           | paris  | boston | marseilles     | prague |
| Cigar   | dannemann | blend  | cain | game       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
