 7. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | october | august | september  | december  |
